  "title": "Temporary Media Assistant (3 - 4 Months)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Convert media files (audio and/or video formats) according to required specifications and file standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all converted files meet quality, format, and naming conventions.</li>\n  <li>Perform general administrative duties to support the project (e.g., documentation updates, tracking sheets, status reporting).</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the project team to ensure timely completion of all conversion tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least a Nitec qualification is required.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Adobe Premiere Pro is required; knowledge of Adobe After Effects is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Prior administrative experience preferred; media or content-related experience is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of media file formats (e.g., MP4, MOV, MP3, WAV) and file-conversion tools.</li>\n</ul>",
